                            <comment id="23472" author="ramseylubbat" created="Fri, 27 Apr 2007 05:19:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix we are using for the errors tag. A similar fix is used for the option tag. The real fix should probably be in the AbstractHtmlElementBodyTag class, but we leave it up to the experts to decide.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="26783" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Sun, 7 Oct 2007 22:49:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This should be fixed in tonight&apos;s 2.5 RC1 snapshot. I&apos;ve revised TagWriter to reobtain the underlying Writer from the PageContext for each write operation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
